    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Semi-schematic line drawings of Aculus lydii n. sp., female: V. Ventral view; AD. Prodorsal shield; IG. Internal genitalia; em. Empodium; LM. Lateral view of microtubercles. Scale bar = 50 Μm for V and AD; 24 Μm for IG; 8 Μm for em; LM enlarged." ;
